                        <p><strong>D</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>k</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>:</strong></p><p>Deret = 7 5 3 1</p><p>a = 7</p><p>b = U2 - U1</p><p>   = 5 - 7</p><p>   = -2</p><p></p><p><strong>D</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>.</strong><strong> </strong><strong>:</strong></p><p>U40 = ?</p><p></p><p><strong>U</strong><strong>n</strong><strong> </strong><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>a</strong><strong> </strong><strong>+</strong><strong> </strong><strong>(</strong><strong>n</strong><strong> </strong><strong>-</strong><strong> </strong><strong>1</strong><strong>)</strong><strong> </strong><strong>b</strong></p><p>U40 = 7 + (40 - 1)(-2)</p><p>U40 = 7 + (39)(-2)</p><p>U40 = 7 + (-78)</p><p><strong>U</strong><strong>4</strong><strong>0</strong><strong> </strong><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>-</strong><strong>7</strong><strong>1</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p>-71<p><strong>Penjelasan dengan langkah-langkah:</strong></p><p>Diketahui :</p>a = 7b = U2-U1  = 5-7 = -2<p>Ditanya : U40=.........?</p><p>Jawab : </p><p>Un : a + ( n- 1 ) b</p><p>      : 7 + ( 40-1 ) (-2)</p><p>      : 7 + ( 39 ) (-2)</p><p>      : 7 + (-78)</p><p>      : -71</p><br />
